<https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.ca/KB/RecordSet/F%204420-6-5> rdfs:label "F 4420-6-5 - William G. Davis international visits: photographs and textual records (Record Set)";
  add:findingAidNote "An online listing of the material in this sub-series is available.";
